v><div class='line' id='LC92'><span class="s2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;もし、サーバが起動していない場合、それらのサーバは安全です。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&quot;</span><span class="p">;</span></div><div class='line' id='LC93'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="nv">$TEXT</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;security-text3&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;&lt;b&gt;よく検討してください:</span></div><div class='line' id='LC94'><span class="s2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;XAMPPのセキュリティを設定すると、いくつかのサンプルが実行できなくなります。もし、あなたがPHPを</span><span class="se">\&quot;</span><span class="s2">safe mode</span><span class="se">\&quot;</span><span class="s2">で使っていた場合、セキュリティ設定のいくつかの機能が動作しません。セキュリティを設定すると、機能が制限される場合があります。&lt;/b&gt;&quot;</span><span class="p">;</span></div><div class='line' id='LC95'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="nv">$TEXT</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;security-text4&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;XAMPPデフォルトのポート:&quot;</span><span class="p">;</span></div><div class='line' id='LC96'><br/></div><div class='line' id='LC97'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="nv">$TEXT</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;security-ok&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;安全&quot;</span><span class="p">;</span></div><div class='line' id='LC98'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="nv">$TEXT</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;security-nok&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;要注意&quot;</span><span class="p">;</span></div><div class='line' id='LC99'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="nv">$TEXT</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;security-noidea&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <sp